<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT44">
<l>koṇṭu kuṭaṅkālmēl vaitta kuḻaviyāy</l>
<l>taṇṭa varakkaṉ talaitāḷāṟ paṇṭeṇṇi</l>
<l>pōṅkumara ṉiṟkum poḻilvēṅ kaṭamalaikkē</l>
<l>pōṅkumara ruḷḷīr purintu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O you young men! Go desiringly to the Vēṅkaṭam hills with groves</l>
<l>where stands the Young Man, who, in former times,</l>
<l>became an infant placed on [Brahmā’s] laps, and</l>
<l>and went on counting the punishable Rākṣasa’ heads with [Its] feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
